        Exercise(name: "Seated Calf Raise", muscle: .calves, description: "Sit at the leg press machine in a manner where just the top part of each foot is touching the bottom of the platform in front of you. Push back as far as you can while keeping your toes connected to the platform. Return and repeat"),
